                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>1999-07-27</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This was an excellent historical record of probably the greatest American that ever lived.  However, it has long, complex, diffcult to read wording that makes it somewhat labor-intensive reading.  The content is great, but  there are far easier to read (and understand) books about Lincoln.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">excellent and concise. had some uncertian facts though.</div>
