                    <span>interesting in that it was written from a british perspective. i have read several biographies on lincoln and would recommend this book as an introductory volume for those who want to study lincoln, but, as an  important volume for those who study general presidential history, civil  war, and general american history. originally published in 1916.</span>
                  
